To install updateports, type "make install."
To deinstall or uninstall updateports, type "make deinstall" or
"make uninstall respectively." Note that deinstalling and uninstalling
does exactly the same thing.

This script supports the following operating systems:
Darwin (Mac OS X)
FreeBSD
Linux
NetBSD
OpenBSD
SunOS (Solaris).

You are free to use and distribute this script under the terms of the 3-clause
BSD license.